products.name: Signature Five-Pocket Jean, Slim Straight
products.qrtxt:
• The slimmest-fit denim we offer, crafted from 100% cotton that just gets better the more you wear it
  • Made for a modern outlook, with whiskering on the legs and hand-sanded finishing
  • Slim Straight: our slimmest pant sits below the natural waist and is fitted through the hips and thighs, with a narrower straight leg below the knee.

products.qrtxt:
